00:45:49,820 --> 00:45:51,201
And go ahead and tell me your name and where you're from.

927
00:45:51,221 --> 00:45:54,483
Hi, John Peeble from Tucson, Arizona.

928
00:45:55,223 --> 00:45:55,984
Great talk, thank you.

929
00:45:57,191 --> 00:46:01,553
Just a quick comment, just played Liberté two weeks ago and pulled off a Royalist win

