941
00:46:24,237 --> 00:46:25,898
So we work a little strangely

942
00:46:26,539 --> 00:46:28,441
compared to other game studios,

943
00:46:28,641 --> 00:46:30,362
so in terms of other publishers.

944
00:46:30,403 --> 00:46:31,524
So we're a little game studio.

945
00:46:31,584 --> 00:46:33,105
We all pretty much work in one room

946
00:46:33,165 --> 00:46:34,747
and then our artist is remote

947
00:46:35,247 --> 00:46:36,888
and we take every product we work on

948
00:46:37,029 --> 00:46:39,271
from the cradle to the grave altogether.

