00:47:53,585 --> 00:47:55,748
is a game for like your uncle or dad, right?

973
00:47:55,768 --> 00:47:57,690
It's like, oh cool, World War II, yes.

974
00:47:58,291 --> 00:48:02,095
So we wanted a theme that really tried to broaden things out.

975
00:48:02,355 --> 00:48:05,138
And so Kyle, we were working on this adventure game,

976
00:48:06,219 --> 00:48:09,203
and Kyle was setting it in this sort of Robin Hood-esque.

