1074
00:52:35,724 --> 00:52:38,566
Because I think that a lot of this has to do

1075
00:52:38,586 --> 00:52:39,526
with the frame of the question.

1076
00:52:39,746 --> 00:52:42,868
So the way I tend to view it is you want to create

1077
00:52:43,288 --> 00:52:45,669
an environment where you are going to be the person

1078
00:52:45,749 --> 00:52:47,050
who is made king.

1079
00:52:47,710 --> 00:52:51,292
And so if you're thinking about a strategy guide,

1080
00:52:51,332 --> 00:52:55,694
for instance, if you're worried about players

