1087
00:53:14,960 --> 00:53:18,541
agreements that are contingent upon the actions of other players.

1088
00:53:19,002 --> 00:53:24,003
So I'll say like, look, hey Turkey, I know you don't want to fight Austria, but if they

1089
00:53:24,063 --> 00:53:25,444
fight me, can you commit?

1090
00:53:26,257 --> 00:53:29,179
And so creating those kinds of informal coalitions

1091
00:53:29,219 --> 00:53:31,680
that will then have inertia to them in the late game

