1108
00:54:20,989 --> 00:54:22,831
if you are going, so like basically,

1109
00:54:23,111 --> 00:54:25,453
if you give people too much tactical flexibility,

1110
00:54:25,994 --> 00:54:27,075
then it's always going,

1111
00:54:27,315 --> 00:54:28,636
it's never gonna be able to tell a story

1112
00:54:28,676 --> 00:54:29,737
because it's always gonna feel

1113
00:54:30,137 --> 00:54:32,119
like there is no inertia to your own choices.

